{"tid":2424583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［回帶鞭屍時間］ 五年前228你做緊乜？","createTime":"2021-02-26T16:32:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T15:06:34.000Z","uid":325346,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"94cc8c5956097afccc0c139c9e0d65ac2a441b83","tid":2424583,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T16:32:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cb3vW5q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcb3vW5q.jpg&h=e11984d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年天琦助選團全部都係學生<br />\n又多謝又有禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當年楊onq的助選團有樣學樣（大媽）<br />\n特別記得當中有分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n轉間眼咁就五年、當年本土派一致支持天琦<br />\n成就天琦66524票高票落敗<br />\n天琦明年出獄，我們都唔可以放棄要唱18俾佢聽<br />\n知冇？<br />\n<br />\n五年後<br />\n國安法生效<br />\nDeadbody無再出現無出過一句聲<br />\n可能準備入獄前要同老婆屌閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131776161ea64ddac71d4fc81bb788ed60c6c7c5","tid":2424583,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T16:38:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鞭鞭鞭<br />\n<br />\nOnq <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b0a87551fed3c5d8cb0253ebe3c19c252f5219","tid":2424583,"uid":59283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T16:41:37.000Z","msg":"黎汶洛直情消失左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867b856b788b0ade81398d9a0547deb57ad21186","tid":2424583,"uid":325346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"99b0a87551fed3c5d8cb0253ebe3c19c252f5219","tid":2424583,"uid":59283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T16:41:37.000Z","msg":"黎汶洛直情消失左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedB